### 测试后端API接口

### 1. 测试基本连接
GET http://localhost:3001/api

### 2. 获取歌曲列表
GET http://localhost:3001/api/songs

### 3. 获取推荐歌曲
GET http://localhost:3001/api/songs/recommended

### 4. 获取热门歌曲
GET http://localhost:3001/api/songs/popular

### 5. 搜索歌曲
GET http://localhost:3001/api/songs/search?keyword=夜曲

### 6. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "name": "测试用户",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456"
}

### 7. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 8. 获取用户信息 (需要先登录获取token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. 获取公开播放列表
GET http://localhost:3001/api/playlists/public

### 10. 创建播放列表 (需要登录)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "我的播放列表",
  "description": "测试播放列表",
  "isPrivate": false
}
